&lt;h2&gt;&lt;font color="#990000"&gt;MBEToolbox Demos&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The MBEToolbox is a collection of MATLAB functions the sequence data 
analyses of molecular biology and evolution. The toolbox can be used to manipulate
aligned sequences, calculate pairwise evolutionary distances, estimate substitution 
rates and conduct statistical analyses of sequences.&lt;/p&gt;
